No problem now.

73
00:06:29,355 --> 00:06:30,879
Mina....

74
00:06:32,725 --> 00:06:35,785
Why isn't Mina getting on?

75
00:06:35,862 --> 00:06:39,195
Forget about that dog.

76
00:06:39,265 --> 00:06:42,530
No, I'll walk it back.

77
00:06:42,902 --> 00:06:47,737
What? It will be dark
when you get to the hospital.

78
00:06:47,807 --> 00:06:51,436
