He is coming back.

104
00:09:04,076 --> 00:09:08,945
You think
this carriage is coming back for you?

105
00:09:11,050 --> 00:09:13,951
That's alright.
I won't force you to take the ride.

106
00:09:18,124 --> 00:09:19,421
Mina.

107
00:09:29,669 --> 00:09:30,966
What happened?

108
00:09:32,738 --> 00:09:35,172
-Mr.Markba's dog?
-No! Mina.

109
00:09:39,579 --> 00:09:41,979
