110
00:09:42,448 --> 00:09:44,177
Oh well....

111
00:09:44,784 --> 00:09:47,685
You are going back to mr.Markba's?

112
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:49,214
You know it?

113
00:09:49,288 --> 00:09:53,224
Not very well. It's always like this
when taking my ride.

114
00:09:53,826 --> 00:09:56,420
Get off.
This is for people.

115
00:09:56,495 --> 00:09:58,053
Get off.

116
00:09:58,631 --> 00:10:02,795
