-Yes.

134
00:11:42,535 --> 00:11:43,934
Blanny.

135
00:11:45,604 --> 00:11:46,901
Blanny.

136
00:11:49,075 --> 00:11:50,440
Candy.

137
00:11:50,810 --> 00:11:53,506
