So sleepy.

236
00:19:38,877 --> 00:19:42,540
I am going to pick the petals.
Please wait for a moment.

237
00:20:02,467 --> 00:20:03,866
Mr.Markba.

238
00:20:04,536 --> 00:20:07,232
Mr.Markba, look! So many...

239
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:10,335
Come on. Let's go back to the room.

240
00:20:13,111 --> 00:20:15,102
These petals....

241
00:20:19,751 --> 00:20:22,185
Mr.Markba.

242
00:20:33,765 --> 00:20:35,528
Mr.Markba.

243
00:20:36,301 --> 00:20:38,394
Wake up, Mr.Marka!

244
00:20:39,238 --> 00:20:42,867
We are going fishing after you recover.
You promised me.

245
00:20:44,509 --> 00:20:46,841
How did this happen?

246
00:20:48,347 --> 00:20:52,784
I took care of you so hard.

247
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:57,147
Mr.Markba.

248
00:21:01,293 --> 00:21:04,854
No matter how we call,
no matter how we cry,

249
00:21:04,930 --> 00:21:07,956
